            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5350,
            "LocalizeKR": "따, 딱히 내가\n틀린 말 한 건 아니잖아?",
            "LocalizeJP": "べ、別に私、\n何も間違ったことは\n言ってないでしょ！？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
